The paper deals with the hard-core lattice gas model, which is a topic in discrete mathematics (cs.DM) and combinatorics (cs.CC). The study of phase transitions is also related to graph theory (cs.GT). The paper presents algorithmic results for approximating the partition function, which is a topic in computational complexity (cs.SI) and information theory (cs.IT).
